The paper also involves program transformation and solving techniques, which are common in the sub-categories of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.PL (Programming Languages). The paper also discusses experiments on verification benchmarks, which falls under the sub-category of cs.SE (Software Engineering).
